column2: VelocityShares Long LIBOR ETN
column37: The investment seeks to be linked to the Janus Velocity Long LIBOR Index (the    Long LIBOR Index   ). The Long LIBOR Index aims to approximate the daily performance of a hypothetical long investment in the composite forward LIBOR rate  as if the composite forward LIBOR rate itself were an asset that could be invested in. It does so by acking the return on a hypothetical short position in Eurodollar futures conacts  where that position is recalibrated daily to result in a return over the next Index Business Day that approximates the percentage change in the composite forward LIBOR rate over that next day  subject to the long LIBOR floor.

column2: VelocityShares Short LIBOR ETN
column37: The Short LIBOR ETNs are linked to the Janus Velocity Short LIBOR Index (the    Short LIBOR Index   ). The Short LIBOR Index aims to approximate the daily performance of a hypothetical short position in the composite forward LIBOR rate  as if the composite forward LIBOR rate itself were an asset that could be shorted. It does so by acking the return on a hypothetical long position in Eurodollar futures conacts  where that position is recalibrated daily to result in a return over the next Index Business Day that approximates the inverse of the percentage change in the composite forward LIBOR rate over that next day  subject to the short LIBOR floor.

YieldShares High Income ETF
column37: The investment seeks to provide investment results that  before fees and expenses  correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the ISE High IncomeTM Index (the 'index').
